verbose_text: Regarding its antibacterial action, in vitro studies demonstrated that HST extract inhibited the growth of Gram negative bacteria including Fusobacterium nucleatum, Porphyromonas gingivalis, Porphyromonas endodontalis, Prevotella intermedia, Prevotella melaninogenica, Tannerella forsythia, Treponema denticola, and Porphyromonas asaccharolytica.
